OL,3,CHair salon owner 'having to sell
OL,4,Cfamily home' to save his business
OL,6,FNathan told ITV News' Sam Blackledge
OL,7,Fhow the economic crisis was affecting
OL,8,Fhis life.
OL,10,FThe owner of a hair salon in east
OL,11,FDevon says he has been forced to sell
OL,12,Fhis family home to keep the business
OL,13,Fafloat.
OL,15,FNathan Plumridge, who runs Energy Hair
OL,16,Fnear Topsham, is calling on the
OL,17,FGovernment to lower VAT rates and is
OL,18,Fwarning the industry faces serious
OL,19,Fproblems if the continues.
