OL,3,CHair salon owner 'having to sell
OL,4,Cfamily home' to save his business
OL,6,F"I never thought I would ever be in
OL,7,Fthe situation where I would be having
OL,8,Fto sell my family home to remove
OL,9,Fcapital to put back into my business,
OL,10,Fto pay debts, pay bills, and get
OL,11,Fmyself back to a level playing field."
OL,13,FNathan said he has worked hard to
OL,14,Fbuild a thriving family business, but
OL,15,Fadmits the financial struggle is
OL,16,Ftaking its toll.J"You're pushing
OL,17,Fyourself to a different place," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
